#[navbar]

#[section, $md:
    @../ (Documentation) / Constants and compile-time behaviour

    # Constants and compile-time behaviour

    Constants move work out of runtime and into the compiler. They are strict on purpose: the value must be known, stable and finished before the program starts.

    Templates can join in too. A const page fragment is just a template with nowhere left to hide.
]

